
Documentation for the modal logic specifications.

Example formula




<logic type="modal">
  <formula name="phi">   
  \mu X . \nu Y. X \vee Y \wedge Z
  </formula>
</logic>




TAGS:

logic 
   attributes: 
      type   specifies the logic used. in this case: modal
   
   
formula
   attributes:
     name  gives the formula a name for future reference
           may be omitted
           
           